Package fr.cs.group12.myFoodora.myFoodora

Class MyFoodoraSystem

java.lang.Object
fr.cs.group12.myFoodora.myFoodora.MyFoodoraSystem
public class MyFoodoraSystem extends Object
This class represents the MyFoodora system, which is a food delivery platform. It is the core of the system. It manages users (restaurants, customers, couriers, and managers), orders, and system configurations.
